description: Mapping of Picfair store images to local gallery images. Each unique imageId appears once with its gallery match (or null if unmatched). Matches were made by visual comparison of Cloudinary thumbnails against gallery image alt text descriptions.

stats.note: 4 gallery images are each matched by 2 different store images (same photo, different Picfair titles or same image in different albums)
